  "title": "Cellphone and Electronics Retail Sales Manager",
  "description": "<p>Job Description:</p><p>We are seeking an experienced Retail Sales Manager to lead our cellphone and electronics sales team in Singapore. The successful candidate will be responsible for driving sales growth, managing a team of sales staff, and providing excellent customer service.</p><p>Responsibilities:</p><p>- Lead and manage a team of sales staff</p><p>- Drive sales growth and achieve targets</p><p>- Provide excellent customer service and resolve issues</p><p>- Manage stock levels, displays, and promotions</p><p>- Analyze sales data and optimize strategies</p><p>- Collaborate with other teams to achieve business goals</p><p>Requirements:</p><p>- 2+ years of retail experience, preferably in electronics or cellphone sales</p><p>- Strong leadership and sales skills</p><p>- Excellent communication and customer service skills</p><p>- Ability to work in a fast-paced environment</p><p>- Relevant sales or business qualifications a plus</p>",
